h2 WTF is this thing?
pre
	code.
		npm i -g printshop
		printshop create my-new-book

p #[dfn printshop] is a simple CLI tool to publish e-books. It allows for export to .pdf, .epub and static site format, because why not.

h3 So, it's like InDesign, but for tech junkies?
p Yup. I got so fucking fed up with InDesign, so I decided to switch to layouting my shit with html and css. Well, with pug and sass, but who cares?

