h2 How to use this shit
p First of all, create a project:
code printshop create my-new-book

p It will create a folder my-new-book, which will look like this:
pre
	code.
		my-new-book
			content/
				index.pug
			fonts/
			images/
				cover.jpg
			scripts/
				print/
					paged_extender.js
				hot_reload.js
			styles/
				print.sass
				web.sass
			templates/
				print.pug
				web.pug
			printshop.config.yaml